---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Prompts & Skills — how we handle your data and use cookies.">
  <main class="container section">
    <div class="legal-content">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="updated">Last updated: February 25, 2026</p>

      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        Prompts & Skills ("we", "us", "our") operates the website
        <a href="https://promptandskills.com">promptandskills.com</a>.
        This page informs you of our policies regarding the collection, use,
        and disclosure of information when you use our site.
      </p>
      <p>
        We do not require registration, login, or any personal information to
        access our content. Our site is free and open to everyone.
      </p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>
        We do not collect personal information directly. However, third-party
        services we use may collect certain data automatically:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Usage Data</strong> — Pages visited, time on page, referral source, browser type, and device information. This data is anonymized and used only to improve the site.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies</strong> — Small data files stored on your device by third-party services (see below).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Google AdSense</h2>
      <p>
        We use Google AdSense to display advertisements. Google AdSense uses
        cookies to serve ads based on your prior visits to our site or other
        websites. Google's use of advertising cookies enables it and its
        partners to serve ads based on your visit to our site and/or other
        sites on the Internet.
      </p>
      <p>
        You may opt out of personalized advertising by visiting
        <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Ads Settings</a>.
        Alternatively, you can opt out of third-party vendor cookies by visiting
        <a href="https://www.aboutads.info/choices/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">aboutads.info</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Google Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        We may use Google Analytics to understand how visitors interact with our
        site. Google Analytics collects anonymized data including pages visited,
        session duration, and geographic region. This data helps us improve
        content and user experience. You can opt out using the
        <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        Our site itself does not set cookies. However, third-party services
        (Google AdSense, Google Analytics) may set cookies on your device.
        These cookies are used for:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Serving relevant advertisements</li>
        <li>Measuring ad performance</li>
        <li>Analyzing site traffic and usage patterns</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        You can control cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers
        allow you to block or delete cookies. Note that blocking cookies may
        affect your experience on some websites.
      </p>

      <h2>Third-Party Links</h2>
      <p>
        Our content may include links to external websites. We are not
        responsible for the privacy practices or content of these third-party
        sites. We encourage you to read the privacy policies of any external
        site you visit.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        Our site is intended for a general audience and does not knowingly
        collect information from children under 13. If you believe a child has
        provided personal information through a third-party service on our
        site, please contact us.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this privacy policy from time to time. Changes will be
        posted on this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you
        to review this page periodically.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this privacy policy, please reach out via
        our GitHub repository at
        <a href="https://github.com/MicroSphere-Systems/PromptsAndSkills" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/MicroSphere-Systems/PromptsAndSkills</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal-content {
    max-width: 48rem;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .updated {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary, #a1a1aa);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary, #e4e4e7);
  }

  h2 {
    font-family: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--accent-green, #00ff88);
  }

  p, li {
    color: var(--text-secondary, #a1a1aa);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  ul {
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  a {
    color: var(--accent-green, #00ff88);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  a:hover {
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
</style>
